high_descs: turn left, walk to the door, turn left
grab the cup on the table
turn left, walk to the refrigerator on the left
open the refrigerator, put the cup in the refrigerator, wait a while, take the cup out
turn right, walk back to the table
put the cup in the coffee machine

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the round table.
Pick up the mug from the table.
Turn left and go to the fridge.
Put the mug in the fridge and then take it out after a bit.
Turn right and head to the round table.
Set the mug into the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Chill a mug for a coffee.

high_descs: Turn to the left and then the left again to find the round table.
Pick up the cup from the coffee maker.
Hold the cup and turn left, and then right to find the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the cup inside. Shut the door, then open it and take the cup out. Shut the fridge door.
Take the cup and turn right, then left to go back to the coffee machine.
Place the cup on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Chill a cup and place it with the coffee maker.
